encia, España","global_code":"8CFXFJ62+WX"},"rating":5,"reference":"ChIJZ7oVRINPYA0RkuqV15W3bE8","reviews":[{"author_name":"PILAR GARCIA","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103163683398772114621/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AD_cMMSZ32rs1mD2tXazKoazbzgAfzhoucAG-5ev5GZxMQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 2 meses","text":"Paula es encantadora, te explica todo muy bien, y te transmite confianza y seguridad. Es amable, simpática y eficiente, un 10 en todo. No habíamos ido nunca a cambiar dinero para viajar a otro país, siempre lo hacemos en el banco, pero sin duda volveremos. Lo recomendamos 100%. Gracias","time":1679596260,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Jesús Martinez Chaparro","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107402644382016242531/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AAcHTtcM25EbajGNJxc_ufQ8d4AqkJvdprBM5I21xYUR=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"en la última semana","text":"Un gran lugar con paula atendiendo  es de agradecer que te atiendan con una sonrrisa y simpatia la verdad de 10 yo sin duda volvere un precio unico","time":1685419207,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Julieta FR","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116574463907879265516/reviews","language":"es","original_language":"es","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AAcHTtetl4bu1vL76CqjMH7HYOFrf1xTUrCU3at3S5YF=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"Hace 2 semanas","text":"Espectacular!. Paula es un encanto, muy atenta y simpática. Pude cambiar USD sin problemas!. Sin dudas volveré.\nMuchas gracias Paula!","time":1684229305,"translated":false},{"author_name":"jorge Lorente Gonzalez","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110874554524873680921/reviews","language":"es","original_lang